name: THESINS//010 : THE END
description:
ACT//010. VILLA ODELLIA.

The feeling of loss after all that happened may never really end. Even I have zero regrets over the end of my relationship with Carl. Tom made me insanely happy, but i never truly get over the fact that i lost my friend because of him. Life i once envisioned is very different from what became my reality. But that’s okay. At the end of the road, there is a feeling of relief came. I made it.
